description: Launched on 15/01/2019 by Currency.com team based in Gibraltar and Belarus, represents a tokenised version of traditional financial market - Lvmh Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton Se shares on Ethereum blockchain, price of underlined assets is tailored to Lvmh Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton Se market price. Tokenisation of the asset provides possibility to invest to popular financial markets worldwide using crypto.
name: Lvmh Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton Se
